[2018/08/24 09:25:45] SQL Query: SELECT t.id_plan,t.nombre,t.promocional,t.duracion,t.extension,t.porc_descarga,t.num_post,t.costo, 
        GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as acciones, GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as descripciones
        FROM mfo_permisoplan p
        INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON a.id_accionSist = p.id_accionSist 
        INNER JOIN mfo_plan t ON t.id_plan = p.id_plan 
        WHERE a.estado = 1
        AND t.tipo_plan = 2
        AND t.tipo_usuario = 1
        AND t.id_sucursal = 1
        GROUP BY t.id_plan
        ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan;
[2018/08/24 09:25:45] SQL Query: SELECT t.id_plan,t.nombre,t.promocional,t.duracion,t.extension,t.porc_descarga,t.num_post,t.costo, 
        GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as acciones, GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as descripciones
        FROM mfo_permisoplan p
        INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON a.id_accionSist = p.id_accionSist 
        INNER JOIN mfo_plan t ON t.id_plan = p.id_plan 
        WHERE a.estado = 1
        AND t.tipo_plan = 1
        AND t.tipo_usuario = 1
        AND t.id_sucursal = 1
        GROUP BY t.id_plan
        ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan;

        GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as acciones, GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as descripciones
        FROM mfo_permisoplan p
        INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON a.id_accionSist = p.id_accionSist 
        INNER JOIN mfo_plan t ON t.id_plan = p.id_plan 
        WHERE a.estado = 1
        AND t.tipo_plan = 2
        AND t.tipo_usuario = 1
        AND t.id_sucursal = 1
        GROUP BY t.id_plan
        ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan;

        GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as acciones, GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as descripciones
        FROM mfo_permisoplan p
        INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON a.id_accionSist = p.id_accionSist 
        INNER JOIN mfo_plan t ON t.id_plan = p.id_plan 
        WHERE a.estado = 1
        AND t.tipo_plan = 1
        AND t.tipo_usuario = 1
        AND t.id_sucursal = 1
        GROUP BY t.id_plan
        ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan;

[2018/08/24 09:31:02] SQL Query: SELECT t.id_plan,t.nombre,t.promocional,t.duracion,t.extension,t.porc_descarga,t.num_post,t.costo, 
        GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as acciones, GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as descripciones
        FROM mfo_permisoplan p
        INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON a.id_accionSist = p.id_accionSist 
        INNER JOIN mfo_plan t ON t.id_plan = p.id_plan 
        WHERE a.estado = 1
        AND t.tipo_plan = 2
        AND t.tipo_usuario = 2
        AND t.id_sucursal = 1
        GROUP BY t.id_plan
        ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan;
[2018/08/24 09:31:02] SQL Query: SELECT t.id_plan,t.nombre,t.promocional,t.duracion,t.extension,t.porc_descarga,t.num_post,t.costo, 
        GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as acciones, GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as descripciones
        FROM mfo_permisoplan p
        INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON a.id_accionSist = p.id_accionSist 
        INNER JOIN mfo_plan t ON t.id_plan = p.id_plan 
        WHERE a.estado = 1
        AND t.tipo_plan = 1
        AND t.tipo_usuario = 2
        AND t.id_sucursal = 1
        GROUP BY t.id_plan
        ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan;

[2018/08/24 09:35:30] SQL Query: SELECT t.id_plan,t.nombre,t.promocional,t.duracion,t.extension,t.porc_descarga,t.num_post,t.costo, 
        GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as acciones, GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as descripciones
        FROM mfo_permisoplan p
        INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON a.id_accionSist = p.id_accionSist 
        INNER JOIN mfo_plan t ON t.id_plan = p.id_plan 
        WHERE a.estado = 1
        AND t.tipo_plan = 2
        AND t.tipo_usuario = 2
        AND t.id_sucursal = 1
        GROUP BY t.id_plan
        ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan;
[2018/08/24 09:35:30] SQL Query: SELECT t.id_plan,t.nombre,t.promocional,t.duracion,t.extension,t.porc_descarga,t.num_post,t.costo, 
        GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as acciones, GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as descripciones
        FROM mfo_permisoplan p
        INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON a.id_accionSist = p.id_accionSist 
        INNER JOIN mfo_plan t ON t.id_plan = p.id_plan 
        WHERE a.estado = 1
        AND t.tipo_plan = 1
        AND t.tipo_usuario = 2
        AND t.id_sucursal = 1
        GROUP BY t.id_plan
        ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan;

[2018/08/24 09:36:17] SQL Query: SELECT t.id_plan,t.nombre,t.promocional,t.duracion,t.extension,t.porc_descarga,t.num_post,t.costo, 
        GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as acciones, GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as descripciones
        FROM mfo_permisoplan p
        INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON a.id_accionSist = p.id_accionSist 
        INNER JOIN mfo_plan t ON t.id_plan = p.id_plan 
        WHERE a.estado = 1
        AND t.tipo_plan = 2
        AND t.tipo_usuario = 2
        AND t.id_sucursal = 1
        GROUP BY t.id_plan
        ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan;
[2018/08/24 09:36:17] SQL Query: SELECT t.id_plan,t.nombre,t.promocional,t.duracion,t.extension,t.porc_descarga,t.num_post,t.costo, 
        GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as acciones, GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as descripciones
        FROM mfo_permisoplan p
        INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON a.id_accionSist = p.id_accionSist 
        INNER JOIN mfo_plan t ON t.id_plan = p.id_plan 
        WHERE a.estado = 1
        AND t.tipo_plan = 1
        AND t.tipo_usuario = 2
        AND t.id_sucursal = 1
        GROUP BY t.id_plan
        ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan;

        GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as acciones, GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as descripciones
        FROM mfo_permisoplan p
        INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON a.id_accionSist = p.id_accionSist 
        INNER JOIN mfo_plan t ON t.id_plan = p.id_plan 
        WHERE a.estado = 1
        AND t.tipo_plan = 2
        AND t.tipo_usuario = 2
        AND t.id_sucursal = 1
        GROUP BY t.id_plan

[2018/08/24 09:36:18] SQL Query: SELECT t.id_plan,t.nombre,t.promocional,t.duracion,t.extension,t.porc_descarga,t.num_post,t.costo, 
        GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as acciones, GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as descripciones
        FROM mfo_permisoplan p
        INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON a.id_accionSist = p.id_accionSist

        WHERE a.estado = 1
        AND t.tipo_plan = 1
        AND t.tipo_usuario = 2
        AND t.id_sucursal = 1
        GROUP BY t.id_plan

[2018/08/24 09:37:50] SQL Query: SELECT t.id_plan,t.nombre,t.promocional,t.duracion,t.extension,t.porc_descarga,t.num_post,t.costo, 
        GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as acciones, GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as descripciones
        FROM mfo_permisoplan p
        INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON a.id_accionSist = p.id_accionSist 
        INNER JOIN mfo_plan t ON t.id_plan = p.id_plan 
        WHERE a.estado = 1
        AND t.tipo_plan = 2
        AND t.tipo_usuario = 2
        AND t.id_sucursal = 1
        GROUP BY t.id_plan
        ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan;
[2018/08/24 09:37:50] SQL Query: SELECT t.id_plan,t.nombre,t.promocional,t.duracion,t.extension,t.porc_descarga,t.num_post,t.costo, 
        GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as acciones, GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as descripciones
        FROM mfo_permisoplan p
        INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON a.id_accionSist = p.id_accionSist 
        INNER JOIN mfo_plan t ON t.id_plan = p.id_plan 
        WHERE a.estado = 1
        AND t.tipo_plan = 1
        AND t.tipo_usuario = 2
        AND t.id_sucursal = 1
        GROUP BY t.id_plan
        ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan;

[2018/08/24 09:38:28] SQL Query: SELECT t.id_plan,t.nombre,t.promocional,t.duracion,t.extension,t.porc_descarga,t.num_post,t.costo, 
        GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as acciones, GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as descripciones
        FROM mfo_permisoplan p
        INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON a.id_accionSist = p.id_accionSist 
        INNER JOIN mfo_plan t ON t.id_plan = p.id_plan 
        WHERE a.estado = 1
        AND t.tipo_plan = 2
        AND t.tipo_usuario = 2
        AND t.id_sucursal = 1
        GROUP BY t.id_plan
        ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan;
[2018/08/24 09:38:28] SQL Query: SELECT t.id_plan,t.nombre,t.promocional,t.duracion,t.extension,t.porc_descarga,t.num_post,t.costo, 
        GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as acciones, GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as descripciones
        FROM mfo_permisoplan p
        INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON a.id_accionSist = p.id_accionSist 
        INNER JOIN mfo_plan t ON t.id_plan = p.id_plan 
        WHERE a.estado = 1
        AND t.tipo_plan = 1
        AND t.tipo_usuario = 2
        AND t.id_sucursal = 1
        GROUP BY t.id_plan
        ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan;

[2018/08/24 09:46:25] SQL Query: SELECT t.id_plan,t.nombre,t.promocional,t.duracion,t.extension,t.porc_descarga,t.num_post,t.costo, 
        GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as acciones, GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as descripciones
        FROM mfo_permisoplan p
        INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON a.id_accionSist = p.id_accionSist 
        INNER JOIN mfo_plan t ON t.id_plan = p.id_plan 
        WHERE a.estado = 1
        AND t.tipo_plan = 2
        AND t.tipo_usuario = 2
        AND t.id_sucursal = 1
        GROUP BY t.id_plan
        ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan;
[2018/08/24 09:46:25] SQL Query: SELECT t.id_plan,t.nombre,t.promocional,t.duracion,t.extension,t.porc_descarga,t.num_post,t.costo, 
        GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as acciones, GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as descripciones
        FROM mfo_permisoplan p
        INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON a.id_accionSist = p.id_accionSist 
        INNER JOIN mfo_plan t ON t.id_plan = p.id_plan 
        WHERE a.estado = 1
        AND t.tipo_plan = 1
        AND t.tipo_usuario = 2
        AND t.id_sucursal = 1
        GROUP BY t.id_plan
        ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan;

[2018/08/27 09:44:34] SQL Query: SELECT * FROM mfo_area
[2018/08/27 09:44:34] SQL Query: SELECT * FROM mfo_provincia
[2018/08/27 09:44:34] SQL Query: SELECT * FROM mfo_jornada
[2018/08/27 09:44:34] SQL Query: SELECT * FROM mfo_tipocontrato
[2018/08/27 09:44:34] SQL Query: SELECT 
        o.id_ofertas, o.titulo, o.descripcion, o.salario, o.fecha_contratacion,o.vacantes,o.anosexp,
    a.nombre AS area, n.descripcion AS nivel, j.nombre AS jornada, p.nombre AS provincia, e.descripcion AS escolaridad, t.descripcion AS contrato, r.confidencial,r.discapacidad,r.residencia, r.edad_maxima,
    r.edad_minima, r.licencia, r.viajar, u.nombres AS empresa
    FROM mfo_oferta o, mfo_usuario u, mfo_requisitooferta r, mfo_escolaridad e, mfo_area a, mfo_nivelInteres n, mfo_jornada j, mfo_ciudad c, 
    mfo_tipocontrato t, mfo_provincia p
    WHERE o.estado = 1 
    AND r.id_requisitoOferta = o.id_requisitoOferta
    AND e.id_escolaridad = o.id_escolaridad
    AND c.id_ciudad = o.id_ciudad
    AND p.id_provincia = c.id_provincia
    AND o.id_usuario=u.id_usuario
    AND a.id_area = o.id_area
    AND n.id_nivelInteres = o.id_nivelInteres

        FROM mfo_permisoplan p
        INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON a.id_accionSist = p.id_accionSist 
        INNER JOIN mfo_plan t ON t.id_plan = p.id_plan 
        WHERE a.estado = 1
        AND t.tipo_plan = 2

        AND t.id_sucursal = 1
        GROUP BY t.id_plan

        FROM mfo_permisoplan p

        WHERE a.estado = 1
        AND t.tipo_plan = 1

        AND t.id_sucursal = 1
        GROUP BY t.id_plan

        FROM mfo_permisoplan p
        INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON a.id_accionSist = p.id_accionSist 
        INNER JOIN mfo_plan t ON t.id_plan = p.id_plan 
        WHERE a.estado = 1
        AND t.tipo_plan = 2

        FROM mfo_permisoplan p

[2018/08/27 09:57:54] SQL Query: SELECT t.id_plan,t.nombre,t.promocional,t.duracion,t.extension,t.porc_descarga,t.num_post,t.costo, 
        GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as acciones, GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as descripciones
        FROM mfo_permisoplan p
        INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON a.id_accionSist = p.id_accionSist 
        INNER JOIN mfo_plan t ON t.id_plan = p.id_plan 
        WHERE a.estado = 1
        AND t.tipo_plan = 2
        AND t.tipo_usuario = 1
        AND t.id_sucursal = 1
        GROUP BY t.id_plan
        ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan;
[2018/08/27 09:57:54] SQL Query: SELECT t.id_plan,t.nombre,t.promocional,t.duracion,t.extension,t.porc_descarga,t.num_post,t.costo, 
        GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as acciones, GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as descripciones
        FROM mfo_permisoplan p
        INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON a.id_accionSist = p.id_accionSist 
        INNER JOIN mfo_plan t ON t.id_plan = p.id_plan 
        WHERE a.estado = 1
        AND t.tipo_plan = 1
        AND t.tipo_usuario = 1
        AND t.id_sucursal = 1
        GROUP BY t.id_plan
        ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan;

[2018/08/27 10:00:05] SQL Query: SELECT t.id_plan,t.nombre,t.promocional,t.duracion,t.extension,t.porc_descarga,t.num_post,t.costo, 
        GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as acciones, GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as descripciones
        FROM mfo_permisoplan p
        INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON a.id_accionSist = p.id_accionSist 
        INNER JOIN mfo_plan t ON t.id_plan = p.id_plan 
        WHERE a.estado = 1
        AND t.tipo_plan = 2
        AND t.tipo_usuario = 1
        AND t.id_sucursal = 1
        GROUP BY t.id_plan
        ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan;
[2018/08/27 10:00:05] SQL Query: SELECT t.id_plan,t.nombre,t.promocional,t.duracion,t.extension,t.porc_descarga,t.num_post,t.costo, 
        GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as acciones, GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan) as descripciones
        FROM mfo_permisoplan p
        INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON a.id_accionSist = p.id_accionSist 
        INNER JOIN mfo_plan t ON t.id_plan = p.id_plan 
        WHERE a.estado = 1
        AND t.tipo_plan = 1
        AND t.tipo_usuario = 1
        AND t.id_sucursal = 1
        GROUP BY t.id_plan
        ORDER BY p.id_permisoPlan;
